nodes.text: Jan-gwa city was a Gungan city on Naboo located by a waterfall. Cad Bane went there to kidnap the Force-sensitive infant Roo-Roo Page for Darth Sidious, but was apprehended by Anakin Skywalker and Ahsoka Tano, who had foreseen his arrival and alerted the family. This event gave the city a bit of local notoriety.
